{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1617,"text":"In December of 2010,"},{"time":5293,"text":"the city of Apatzing치n"},{"time":7110,"text":"in the coastal state of Michoac치n, in Mexico,"},{"time":10262,"text":"awoke to gunfire."},{"time":12632,"text":"For two straight days,"},{"time":14208,"text":"the city became an open battlefield"},{"time":16626,"text":"between the federal forces"},{"time":18410,"text":"and a well-organized group,"},{"time":20079,"text":"presumably from the local criminal organization,"},{"time":22862,"text":"La Familia Michoacana, or the Michoac치n family."},{"time":26234,"text":"The citizens didn't only experience incessant gunfire"},{"time":29384,"text":"but also explosions"},{"time":31804,"text":"and burning trucks used as barricades across the city,"},{"time":35075,"text":"so truly like a battlefield."},{"time":37092,"text":"After these two days,"},{"time":38622,"text":"and during a particularly intense encounter,"},{"time":41427,"text":"it was presumed that the leader of La Familia Michoacana,"},{"time":43994,"text":"Nazario Moreno, was killed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46499,"text":"In response to this terrifying violence,"},{"time":48510,"text":"the mayor of Apatzing치n"},{"time":50509,"text":"decided to call the citizens to a march for peace."},{"time":52809,"text":"The idea was to ask for a softer approach"},{"time":56156,"text":"to criminal activity in the state."},{"time":58574,"text":"And so, the day of the scheduled procession,"},{"time":61768,"text":"thousands of people showed up."},{"time":63622,"text":"As the mayor was preparing to deliver"},{"time":65316,"text":"the speech starting the march,"},{"time":67427,"text":"his team noticed"},{"time":68929,"text":"that, while half of the participants"},{"time":72087,"text":"were appropriately dressed in white,"},{"time":73762,"text":"and bearing banners asking for peace,"},{"time":76602,"text":"the other half was actually marching"},{"time":78771,"text":"in support of the criminal organization"},{"time":81862,"text":"and its now-presumed-defunct leader."},{"time":85046,"text":"Shocked, the mayor decided to step aside"},{"time":88115,"text":"rather than participate or lead a procession"},{"time":90126,"text":"that was ostensibly in support of organized crime."},{"time":93511,"text":"And so his team stepped aside."},{"time":95753,"text":"The two marches joined together,"},{"time":97829,"text":"and they continued their path"},{"time":100834,"text":"towards the state capital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103444,"text":"This story of horrific violence"},{"time":108255,"text":"followed by a fumbled approach"},{"time":110452,"text":"by federal and local authorities as they tried"},{"time":112647,"text":"to engage civil society,"},{"time":114070,"text":"who has been very well engaged by a criminal organization,"},{"time":117426,"text":"is a perfect metaphor for what's happening in Mexico today,"},{"time":120890,"text":"where we see that our current understanding"},{"time":124239,"text":"of drug violence and what leads to it"},{"time":126607,"text":"is probably at the very least incomplete."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129209,"text":"If you decided to spend 30 minutes trying"},{"time":131212,"text":"to figure out what's going on with drug violence in Mexico"},{"time":133242,"text":"by, say, just researching online,"},{"time":135881,"text":"the first thing you would find out is that"},{"time":137722,"text":"while the laws state that all Mexican citizens are equal,"},{"time":141689,"text":"there are some that are more"},{"time":142808,"text":"and there are some that are much less equal than others,"},{"time":146167,"text":"because you will quickly find out"},{"time":147418,"text":"that in the past six years"},{"time":149122,"text":"anywhere between 60 and 100,000 people"},{"time":151270,"text":"have lost their lives in drug-related violence."},{"time":154828,"text":"To put these numbers in perspective,"},{"time":156575,"text":"this is eight times larger than the number of casualties"},{"time":159391,"text":"in the Iraq and Afghanistan wars combined."},{"time":163912,"text":"It's also shockingly close to the number of people"},{"time":166416,"text":"who have died in the Syrian civil war,"},{"time":168942,"text":"which is an active civil war."},{"time":171155,"text":"This is happening just south of the border."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174351,"text":"Now as you're reading, however,"},{"time":175955,"text":"you will be maybe surprised that you will quickly"},{"time":177638,"text":"become numb to the numbers of deaths,"},{"time":179674,"text":"because you will see that these are sort of abstract numbers"},{"time":183360,"text":"of faceless, nameless dead people."},{"time":186953,"text":"Implicitly or explicitly, there is a narrative"},{"time":189677,"text":"that all the people who are dying"},{"time":191512,"text":"were somehow involved in the drug trade,"},{"time":194368,"text":"and we infer this because they were either tortured"},{"time":197964,"text":"or executed in a professional manner,"},{"time":200125,"text":"or, most likely, both."},{"time":201777,"text":"And so clearly they were criminals"},{"time":203758,"text":"because of the way they died."},{"time":206373,"text":"And so the narrative is that somehow these people"},{"time":208936,"text":"got what they were deserved."},{"time":210179,"text":"They were part of the bad guys."},{"time":212630,"text":"And that creates some form of comfort"},{"time":215178,"text":"for a lot of people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216810,"text":"However, while it's easier to think"},{"time":219774,"text":"of us, the citizens, the police, the army,"},{"time":223759,"text":"as the good guys, and them, the narcos,"},{"time":227331,"text":"the carteles, as the bad guys,"},{"time":230625,"text":"if you think about it,"},{"time":231791,"text":"the latter are only providing a service to the former."},{"time":235599,"text":"Whether we like it or not,"},{"time":237714,"text":"the U.S. is the largest market"},{"time":240375,"text":"for illegal substances in the world,"},{"time":241993,"text":"accounting for more than half of global demand."},{"time":245047,"text":"It shares thousands of miles of border with Mexico"},{"time":248307,"text":"that is its only route of access from the South,"},{"time":251425,"text":"and so, as the former dictator of Mexico, Porfirio Diaz,"},{"time":254480,"text":"used to say, \"Poor Mexico,"},{"time":257209,"text":"so far from God and so close to the United States.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":263401,"text":"The U.N. estimates that there are 55 million users"},{"time":266250,"text":"of illegal drugs in the United States."},{"time":268717,"text":"Using very, very conservative assumptions,"},{"time":271143,"text":"this yields a yearly drug market on the retail side"},{"time":274240,"text":"of anywhere between 30 and 150 billion dollars."},{"time":277023,"text":"If we assume that the narcos only have access"},{"time":279692,"text":"to the wholesale part, which we know is false,"},{"time":282416,"text":"that still leaves you with yearly revenues"},{"time":284757,"text":"of anywhere between 15 billion and 60 billion dollars."},{"time":289275,"text":"To put these numbers in perspective,"},{"time":291191,"text":"Microsoft has yearly revenues of 60 billion dollars."},{"time":295984,"text":"And it so happens that this is a product that,"},{"time":298490,"text":"because of its nature, a business model"},{"time":301465,"text":"to address this market requires you"},{"time":304219,"text":"to guarantee to your producers"},{"time":306348,"text":"that their product will be reliably placed"},{"time":308966,"text":"in the markets where it is consumed."},{"time":311083,"text":"And the only way to do this, because it's illegal,"},{"time":314640,"text":"is to have absolute control of the geographic corridors"},{"time":317650,"text":"that are used to transport drugs."},{"time":319949,"text":"Hence the violence."},{"time":322466,"text":"If you look at a map of cartel influence and violence,"},{"time":325498,"text":"you will see that it almost perfectly aligns"},{"time":327618,"text":"with the most efficient routes of transportation"},{"time":329402,"text":"from the south to the north."},{"time":331297,"text":"The only thing that the cartels are doing"},{"time":332453,"text":"is that they're trying to protect their business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335204,"text":"It's not only a multi-billion dollar market,"},{"time":337629,"text":"but it's also a complex one."},{"time":339724,"text":"For example, the coca plant is a fragile plant"},{"time":342448,"text":"that can only grow in certain latitudes,"},{"time":344764,"text":"and so it means that a business model"},{"time":346500,"text":"to address this market requires you to have"},{"time":348235,"text":"decentralized, international production,"},{"time":350756,"text":"that by the way needs to have good quality control,"},{"time":353300,"text":"because people need a good high"},{"time":355801,"text":"that is not going to kill them"},{"time":357386,"text":"and that is going to be delivered to them when they need it."},{"time":360248,"text":"And so that means they need to secure"},{"time":362241,"text":"production and quality control in the south,"},{"time":365143,"text":"and you need to ensure that you have"},{"time":367150,"text":"efficient and effective distribution channels"},{"time":369642,"text":"in the markets where these drugs are consumed."},{"time":373081,"text":"I urge you, but only a little bit,"},{"time":374672,"text":"because I don't want to get you in trouble,"},{"time":376883,"text":"to just ask around and see how difficult it would be"},{"time":380169,"text":"to get whatever drug you want, wherever you want it,"},{"time":383026,"text":"whenever you want it, anywhere in the U.S.,"},{"time":385971,"text":"and some of you may be surprised to know"},{"time":388784,"text":"that there are many dealers that offer a service"},{"time":390798,"text":"where if you send them a text message,"},{"time":392622,"text":"they guarantee delivery of the drug"},{"time":394327,"text":"in 30 minutes or less."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397209,"text":"Think about this for a second."},{"time":399630,"text":"Think about the complexity"},{"time":401361,"text":"of the distribution network that I just described."},{"time":404761,"text":"It's very difficult to reconcile this"},{"time":407259,"text":"with the image of faceless, ignorant goons"},{"time":411381,"text":"that are just shooting each other,"},{"time":413986,"text":"very difficult to reconcile."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415674,"text":"Now, as a business professor, and as any business professor would tell you,"},{"time":419003,"text":"an effective organization requires"},{"time":421678,"text":"an integrated strategy that includes"},{"time":423587,"text":"a good organizational structure, good incentives,"},{"time":426460,"text":"a solid identity and good brand management."},{"time":429452,"text":"This leads me to the second thing that you would learn"},{"time":431587,"text":"in your 30-minute exploration of drug violence in Mexico."},{"time":434487,"text":"Because you would quickly realize,"},{"time":436049,"text":"and maybe be confused by the fact,"},{"time":437712,"text":"that there are three organizations"},{"time":438949,"text":"that are constantly named in the articles."},{"time":442484,"text":"You will hear about Los Zetas,"},{"time":444558,"text":"the Knights Templar, which is the new brand"},{"time":446529,"text":"for the Familia Michoacana that I spoke about at the beginning,"},{"time":449387,"text":"and the Sinaloa Federation."},{"time":451761,"text":"You will read that Los Zetas is this assortment"},{"time":454552,"text":"of sociopaths that terrify the cities that they enter"},{"time":458907,"text":"and they silence the press,"},{"time":461033,"text":"and this is somewhat true, or mostly true."},{"time":464407,"text":"But this is the result of a very careful branding"},{"time":468486,"text":"and business strategy."},{"time":470287,"text":"You see, Los Zetas is not just"},{"time":472456,"text":"this random assortment of individuals,"},{"time":474256,"text":"but was actually created by another criminal organization, the Gulf Cartel,"},{"time":477911,"text":"that used to control the eastern corridor of Mexico."},{"time":480923,"text":"When that corridor became contested, they decided"},{"time":483337,"text":"that they wanted to recruit"},{"time":485127,"text":"a professional enforcement arm."},{"time":487958,"text":"So they recruited Los Zetas:"},{"time":491567,"text":"an entire unit of elite paratroopers"},{"time":494325,"text":"from the Mexican Army."},{"time":497342,"text":"They were incredibly effective as enforcers for the Gulf Cartel,"},{"time":501048,"text":"so much so that at some point, they decided"},{"time":502936,"text":"to just take over the operations,"},{"time":505429,"text":"which is why I ask you to never keep tigers as pets,"},{"time":509223,"text":"because they grow up."},{"time":511864,"text":"Because the Zetas organization was founded in treason,"},{"time":515560,"text":"they lost some of the linkages to the production and distribution"},{"time":518496,"text":"in the most profitable markets like cocaine,"},{"time":520703,"text":"but what they did have,"},{"time":521993,"text":"and this is again based on their military origin,"},{"time":524453,"text":"was a perfectly structured chain of command"},{"time":527300,"text":"with a very clear hierarchy"},{"time":529925,"text":"and a very clear promotion path that allowed them"},{"time":533989,"text":"to supervise and operate across many, many markets"},{"time":537811,"text":"very effectively,"},{"time":539453,"text":"which is the essence of what a chain of command seeks to do."},{"time":543252,"text":"And so because they didn't have access"},{"time":544541,"text":"to the more profitable drug markets,"},{"time":546876,"text":"this pushed them and gave them the opportunity"},{"time":548549,"text":"to diversify into other forms of crime."},{"time":552047,"text":"That includes kidnapping, prostitution,"},{"time":556102,"text":"local drug dealing and human trafficking,"},{"time":558283,"text":"including of migrants that go from the south to the U.S."},{"time":562239,"text":"So what they currently run is truly"},{"time":566487,"text":"and quite literally a franchise business."},{"time":570059,"text":"They focus most of their recruiting on the army,"},{"time":573890,"text":"and they very openly advertise for better salaries,"},{"time":576967,"text":"better benefits, better promotion paths,"},{"time":579665,"text":"not to mention much better food,"},{"time":581313,"text":"than what the army can deliver."},{"time":584020,"text":"The way they operate is that"},{"time":585889,"text":"when they arrive in a locality,"},{"time":587794,"text":"they let people know that they are there,"},{"time":589545,"text":"and they go to the most powerful local gang"},{"time":592615,"text":"and they say, \"I offer you"},{"time":594855,"text":"to be the local representative of the Zeta brand.\""},{"time":598044,"text":"If they agree -- and you don't want to know"},{"time":599917,"text":"what happens if they don't --"},{"time":601660,"text":"they train them and they supervise them"},{"time":603347,"text":"on how to run the most efficient criminal operation"},{"time":606674,"text":"for that town, in exchange for royalties."},{"time":610175,"text":"This kind of business model obviously depends"},{"time":612081,"text":"entirely on having a very effective brand of fear,"},{"time":614478,"text":"and so Los Zetas"},{"time":616851,"text":"carefully stage acts of violence"},{"time":619144,"text":"that are spectacular in nature,"},{"time":621077,"text":"especially when they arrive first in a city,"},{"time":623877,"text":"but again, that's just a brand strategy."},{"time":627111,"text":"I'm not saying they're not violent,"},{"time":629010,"text":"but what I am saying is that even though you will read"},{"time":630953,"text":"that they are the most violent of all,"},{"time":632816,"text":"when you count, when you do the body count,"},{"time":635779,"text":"they're actually all the same."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639551,"text":"In contrast to them, the Knights Templar"},{"time":642639,"text":"that arose in Michoac치n"},{"time":644479,"text":"emerged in reaction to the incursion"},{"time":647086,"text":"of the Zetas into the state of Michoac치n."},{"time":649621,"text":"Michoac치n is a geographically strategic state"},{"time":652538,"text":"because it has one of the largest ports in Mexico,"},{"time":654541,"text":"and it has very direct routes to the center of Mexico,"},{"time":657132,"text":"which then gives you direct access to the U.S."},{"time":660198,"text":"The Knights Templar realized very quickly"},{"time":661737,"text":"that they couldn't face the Zetas on violence alone,"},{"time":665245,"text":"and so they developed a strategy"},{"time":667602,"text":"as a social enterprise."},{"time":670381,"text":"They brand themselves as representative of"},{"time":673381,"text":"and protecting of the citizens of Michoac치n"},{"time":676037,"text":"against organized crime."},{"time":678335,"text":"Their brand of social enterprise means"},{"time":680066,"text":"that they require a lot of civic engagement,"},{"time":682117,"text":"so they invest heavily in providing local services,"},{"time":686283,"text":"like dealing with home violence,"},{"time":689781,"text":"going after petty criminals, treating addicts,"},{"time":693557,"text":"and keeping drugs out of the local markets"},{"time":696335,"text":"where they are,"},{"time":698815,"text":"and, of course, protecting people"},{"time":700434,"text":"from other criminal organizations."},{"time":702925,"text":"Now, they kill a lot of people too,"},{"time":705956,"text":"but when they kill them,"},{"time":708068,"text":"they provide very careful narratives and descriptions"},{"time":710968,"text":"for why they did them,"},{"time":712220,"text":"through newspaper insertions, YouTube videos,"},{"time":716183,"text":"and billboards that explain that the people who were killed"},{"time":718649,"text":"were killed because they represented a threat"},{"time":720977,"text":"not to us, as an organization, of course,"},{"time":722833,"text":"but to you, as citizens."},{"time":724769,"text":"And so we're actually here to protect you."},{"time":727225,"text":"They, as social enterprises do,"},{"time":729789,"text":"have created a moral and ethical code"},{"time":731289,"text":"that they advertise around,"},{"time":733658,"text":"and they have very strict recruiting practices."},{"time":736796,"text":"And here you have the types of explanations"},{"time":738619,"text":"that they provide for some of their actions."},{"time":742560,"text":"They have actually retained access"},{"time":744456,"text":"to the profitable drug trade,"},{"time":746756,"text":"but the way they do it is, because they control all of Michoac치n,"},{"time":748966,"text":"and they control the Port of L치zaro C치rdenas,"},{"time":751109,"text":"they leverage that to, for example,"},{"time":752911,"text":"trade copper from Michoac치n that is legally created"},{"time":756468,"text":"and legally extracted"},{"time":757868,"text":"with illegal ephedrine from China"},{"time":759870,"text":"which is a critical precursor for methamphetamines"},{"time":763294,"text":"that they produce, and then they have partnerships"},{"time":765694,"text":"with larger organizations like the Sinaloa Federation"},{"time":768232,"text":"that place their products in the U.S."}]},{"cues":[{"time":770922,"text":"Finally, the Sinaloa Federation."},{"time":773593,"text":"When you read about them, you will often read about them"},{"time":775791,"text":"with an undertone of reverence and admiration,"},{"time":779491,"text":"because they are the most integrated"},{"time":781407,"text":"and the largest of all the Mexican organizations,"},{"time":783695,"text":"and, many people argue, the world."},{"time":787149,"text":"They started as just sort of a transport organization"},{"time":790133,"text":"that specialized in smuggling between the U.S."},{"time":792207,"text":"and the Mexican borders,"},{"time":794332,"text":"but now they have grown"},{"time":795750,"text":"into a truly integrated multinational"},{"time":799176,"text":"that has partnerships in production in the south"},{"time":801482,"text":"and partnerships in global distribution"},{"time":804495,"text":"across the planet."},{"time":806989,"text":"They have cultivated a brand of professionalism,"},{"time":810319,"text":"business acumen and innovation."},{"time":813637,"text":"They have designed new drug products"},{"time":815736,"text":"and new drug processes."},{"time":817459,"text":"They have designed narco-tunnels"},{"time":819677,"text":"that go across the border,"},{"time":821218,"text":"and you can see that these are not"},{"time":823033,"text":"\"The Shawshank Redemption\" types."},{"time":826981,"text":"They have invented narco-submarines and boats"},{"time":830677,"text":"that are not detected by radar."},{"time":833360,"text":"They have invented drones to transport drugs,"},{"time":835923,"text":"catapults, you name it."},{"time":839209,"text":"One of the leaders of the Sinaloa Federation"},{"time":841550,"text":"actually made it to the Forbes list."}]},{"cues":[{"time":843988,"text":"[#701 Joaquin Guzman Loera]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":845961,"text":"Like any multinational would, they have specialized"},{"time":848866,"text":"and focused only in the most profitable part of the business,"},{"time":851155,"text":"which is high-margin drugs like cocaine,"},{"time":853833,"text":"heroine, methamphetamines."},{"time":856118,"text":"Like any traditional Latin American multinational would,"},{"time":858691,"text":"the way they control their operations"},{"time":860432,"text":"is through family ties."},{"time":862214,"text":"When they're entering a new market, they send"},{"time":864159,"text":"a family member to supervise it,"},{"time":865880,"text":"or, if they're partnering with a new organization,"},{"time":868697,"text":"they create a family tie,"},{"time":870117,"text":"either through marriages or other types of ties."},{"time":874583,"text":"Like any other multinational would,"},{"time":876746,"text":"they protect their brand by outsourcing"},{"time":879913,"text":"the more questionable parts of the business model,"},{"time":882081,"text":"like for example, when they have to engage"},{"time":884124,"text":"in violence against other criminal organizations,"},{"time":886889,"text":"they recruit gangs and other smaller players"},{"time":890334,"text":"to do the dirty work for them,"},{"time":892133,"text":"and they try to separate their operations"},{"time":893918,"text":"and their violence and be very discrete about this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":897553,"text":"To further strengthen their brand,"},{"time":900049,"text":"they actually have professional P.R. firms"},{"time":902942,"text":"that shape how the press talks about them."},{"time":905421,"text":"They have professional videographers on staff."},{"time":908972,"text":"They have incredibly productive ties"},{"time":911085,"text":"with the security organizations"},{"time":912918,"text":"on both sides of the border."}]},{"cues":[{"time":916330,"text":"And so, differences aside,"},{"time":918931,"text":"what these three organizations share"},{"time":922486,"text":"is on the one hand, a very clear understanding"},{"time":926126,"text":"that institutions cannot be imposed from the top,"},{"time":929210,"text":"but rather they are built from the bottom up"},{"time":932150,"text":"one interaction at a time."},{"time":935433,"text":"They have created extremely coherent structures"},{"time":937854,"text":"that they use to show the inconsistencies"},{"time":940688,"text":"in government policies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944715,"text":"And so what I want you to remember from this talk"},{"time":947202,"text":"are three things."},{"time":948735,"text":"The first one is that drug violence"},{"time":951791,"text":"is actually the result"},{"time":953668,"text":"of a huge market demand"},{"time":956919,"text":"and an institutional setup that forces"},{"time":960569,"text":"the servicing of this market to necessitate violence"},{"time":963695,"text":"to guarantee delivery routes."},{"time":967740,"text":"The second thing I want you to remember"},{"time":969666,"text":"is that these are sophisticated,"},{"time":971612,"text":"coherent organizations"},{"time":974535,"text":"that are business organizations,"},{"time":976493,"text":"and analyzing them and treating them as such"},{"time":978412,"text":"is probably a much more useful approach."},{"time":981801,"text":"The third thing I want you to remember"},{"time":983937,"text":"is that even though we're more comfortable"},{"time":985365,"text":"with this idea of \"them,\""},{"time":987888,"text":"a set of bad guys separated from us,"},{"time":990629,"text":"we are actually accomplices to them,"},{"time":993606,"text":"either through our direct consumption"},{"time":995995,"text":"or through our acceptance of the inconsistency"},{"time":1000067,"text":"between our policies of prohibition"},{"time":1002335,"text":"and our actual behavior of tolerance"},{"time":1005283,"text":"or even encouragement of consumption."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1009507,"text":"These organizations service, recruit from,"},{"time":1013527,"text":"and operate within our communities,"},{"time":1015855,"text":"so necessarily, they are much more integrated"},{"time":1018273,"text":"within them than we are comfortable acknowledging."},{"time":1022743,"text":"And so to me the question is not whether"},{"time":1025608,"text":"these dynamics will continue the way they have."},{"time":1028889,"text":"We see that the nature of this phenomenon"},{"time":1031654,"text":"guarantees that they will."},{"time":1034122,"text":"The question is whether we are willing to continue"},{"time":1037002,"text":"our support of a failed strategy"},{"time":1041608,"text":"based on our stubborn, blissful, voluntary ignorance"},{"time":1047115,"text":"at the cost of the deaths of thousands of our young."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052076,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1053807,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}